<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Facilities</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel three-sm">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p>Salford Royal is easily accessible by public transport. If you are travelling by bus, train or tram, you can find further details on how to get to us and where to park/ammenities on our website via the link below:<br/>http://www.srft.nhs.uk/useful-information/how-to-get-to-the-hospital/</p>
</div>
