<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxyc577d6fa0c114bb68493b38451e386b9-1">Accessibility</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="no">Braille translation service<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled WC<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Induction loop<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Text Relay <span>(Don't know)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Signing service available<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Wheelchair access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Step free access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContenta0a374d8329045df81b7651e3a2e9b8d">
</div>
<p>Why not try our <a href="http://www.srft.nhs.uk/useful-information/how-to-get-to-the-hospital/parking/meetgreet/" title="meet and greet service">Meet and Greet service</a>, where patients or carers can book a volunteer to support them getting to and from their appointment at the hospital.</p>
