<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxyc577d6fa0c114bb68493b38451e386b9-7">Parking</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Car Parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Cycle parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent25faa19979e343148159054e7d6a2a34">
</div>
<p>Parking for disabled people: Spaces are available on the visitors' car park. Drivers may drop-off disabled passengers at other points but must park on the visitors' car park. Anyone needing assistance from their car into the Hospital should telephone in advance or ask at the car park barrier.</p>
